      "type": "leetcode",
      "category": "window",
      "categoryTitle": "Sliding window",
      "title": "Longest Substring Without Repeating",
      "description": "Длина longest substring без повторяющихся символов.",
      "approach": "Sliding window + HashMap с последним индексом символа.",
      "pattern": "Sliding window",
      "leetcodeUrl": "https://leetcode.com/problems/longest-substring-without-repeating-characters/",
      "leetcodeLabel": "3",
      "complexity": "O(n)",
      "algorithm": "Sliding window + HashMap last index",
      "code": "public int maxTransactions(int[] timestamps, int n) {\n    int left = 0, maxCount = 0;\n    for (int right = 0; right < timestamps.length; right++) {\n        while (timestamps[right] - timestamps[left] > n) left++;\n        maxCount = Math.max(maxCount, right - left + 1);\n    }\n    return maxCount;\n}",
      "searchText": "Longest Substring Without Repeating Длина longest substring без повторяющихся символов. Sliding window практика"
    },
